OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnion leader calls for Raab
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be suspended            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Deputy Prime Minister Dominic Raab     
OL,6, should be suspended while he is        
OL,7, investigated over bullying allegations,
OL,8, a civil service union leader has said. 
OL,10,FFDA general secretary Dave Penman told 
OL,11,Fthe BBC: "If that was any other        
OL,12,Femployee... they would in all          
OL,13,Flikelihood be suspended from their     
OL,14,Fjob."                                  
OL,16,FHe said suspension - also backed by    
OL,17,FLabour and the Liberal Democrats -     
OL,18,Fwould help protect current employees.  
OL,20,FMr Raab, who is also justice secretary,
OL,21,Fhas denied bullying civil servants.    
